description:
Description :
        Yang Yunfan is a medical prodigy who is also well versed in Daoism. His journey takes him places, saving people, helping the world, and destroying Mount Zu, all the while showing off his prowess in medicine. “Other doctors can only save people. As for me, I want to save the entire world!”
